oups together similar users and tags that are very â€śactiveâ€ťduring the same time periods. Emphasis is given on usingvarying time scales, so that we distinguish between clustersthat are robust at many time scales and clusters that are somehowoccasional, i.e. they emerge, only at a specific time period.&lt;/p&gt;
